Provisioners 
They can be local , remote and files.
local [execution] they can be executed in local [i.e your own computer - git bash]
Remote [execution] they can be executed in remote [ ec2 instance]
files -  this can be used to copy files from local to remote [ec2]


This can be given in two was 
1. within the resource   - this wont tracked by terrafoem statefile
2. another is by creating null resource - this will be tracked by statefile
